<div id="review_336906885" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/336906885" />
    <a title="Maddux" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5026570-maddux"><img alt="Maddux" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1590693019p2/5026570.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/336906885?book_show_action=true">May 26, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Maddux" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Maddux" href="/user/show/5026570-maddux">Maddux</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer336906885" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8241966130814472675">I read this years ago... can&apos;t remember when. It started the change in the way I communicated with my horses. <br/><br/>Monty Roberts&apos; story - his life - is devoted to the horse. <br/><br/>For non-horse people, it&apos;s an interesting read. <br/><br/>For horse people... it could be the turning point in your equine relationships.<br/><br/></span>
  <span id="freeText8241966130814472675" style="display:none">I read this years ago... can't remember when. It started the change in the way I communicated with my horses. <br /><br />Monty Roberts' story - his life - is devoted to the horse. <br /><br />For non-horse people, it's an interesting read. <br /><br />For horse people... it could be the turning point in your equine relationships.<br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="8241966130814472675" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

